\id JOL
\h Yuwil
\toc1 Yuwil
\toc2 Yuwil
\toc3 Yuw.
\mt1 Yuwil
\c 1
\s1 Ass n SIDI iqarreb-dd
\m 
\v 1 Awař n SIDI i dd-yusin ɣar Yuwil, mmis n Fatu’il. \f ◼ \fr 1:1 \fk Yuwil\ft - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni Arebbi nnes SIDI’. \fk Fatwiyil\ft - isem-a wanita ixs ad yini ‘nneyyet yarezmen n Arebbi’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 2 “Sřem aya, \add a\add* iwessura, sḥessem, marra \add kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n temmurt! Ma imsar uya \add ɛemmarṣ\add* deg wussan nwem niɣ deg wussan n řejdud nwem? \f ◼ \fr 1:2 \fk iwessura\ft - xzar ɛawed Aɛwd. 32:7. \fk imezdaɣ n temmurt\ft - nitni d imezdaɣ n Yahuda (xzar Yuwil 3:1, 20).\f*
\v 3 Ḥajam iḥenjiren nwem x uya u \add jjem\add* iḥenjiren nwem \add ad t ḥajan\add* i iḥenjiren nsen u iḥenjiren nsen i jjiř i dd ɣa yasen.
\v 4 Min ijja bu-weqḍeɛ, tecca i-t tmurɣi, min tejja tmurɣi, icca i-t bu-weřsaḥ, min ijja bu-weřsaḥ, icca i-t bu-uṣard.”
\m 
\v 5 “Faqem, \add kenniw\add* iskarjiyyen, trum, sɣuyyem, marra inni isessen binu, zi ssibbet n binu ẓemmen t jdid, maɣar ittwaqḍeɛ zeg uqemmum nwem.
\v 6 Maɣar ijj n řgens igeɛɛed ḍidd i temmurt inu. Ɣares tizemmar u \add řqedd nnes\add* břa řeḥsab. Tiɣmas nnes \add am\add* teɣmas n wayraden u tiɣmas n teɣmart nnes \add am\add* tinni n teyradt.
\v 7 Aqa yarra tzayart inu d \add ict n řqecɛet n\add* unexřiɛ u yarza wartu inu, yarra i-t qaɛ d aqeccar uca inḍar i-t, tiseḍwin nnes dewřent d ticemřařin.
\v 8 Cetcat am yict n teɛzarect tenni ibeysen s ict n txancet \add n wecḍan\add* x weryaz n temẓi nnes.
\v 9 Tᵉttwaqḍeɛ tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibt n useyyeb zi Taddart n SIDI. Ikehhanen, imsexxaren n SIDI, ceṭṭen.
\v 10 Aqa ittwareddeǧ yiyyar, tecḍen temmurt, minzi imendi iḍeyyeɛ, yuẓeɣ binu n jdid, tejmed zzect.
\v 11 Seḍḥam, kenniw ifeǧaḥen, sɣuyem, kenniw ayt n tzayart, x yirden d imendi, maɣar ṣṣabet n yiyyar tweddar.
\v 12 Tazayart tuẓeɣ, artu n tazart isřaw, tacejjart n aremman, uřa d tini d tcejjart n tteffaḥt, \add wah,\add* marra ticejjura n yiyyar sřawent, ɛad řefraḥet n tarwa n bnadem truḥ.”
\m 
\v 13 “Beysem ixef nwem u wtem agejdur, \add kenniw\add* ikehhanen! Syuyyem \add kenniw\add* imsexxaren n uɛalṭar, asem-dd u tessensem di txuncay \add n wecḍan\add*, \add kenniw\add* imsexxaren n AREBBI, maɣar tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tewhibt n useyyeb ttwakksent i Taddart n AREBBI nwem.
\v 14 Ɛeřmem i yijj n uẓummi iqeddes, barrḥem s yijj n umuni ifarzen, smunem imɣaren d marra imezdaɣ n temmurt di Taddart n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, u řaɣam ɣar SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Yuw. 2:15\x*
\m 
\v 15 “Wih, ass nni! Minzi yudes-dd wass n SIDI u ad dd-yas \add ass nni\add* am yijj n ureddeǧ n Uzemmar x kuřci. \x ◘ \xo 1:15 \xt Ica. 13:6\x*
\v 16 Ma war d aneɣ tᵉttwakkes macca jar tiṭṭawin nneɣ? Uřa d řefraḥet d arcuq zi Taddart n AREBBI nneɣ.
\v 17 Iɛeqqayen n zzariɛet uẓɣen sadu ibursa, ixxamen n řexzen ttwareddǧen, řehrit hedmen, minzi imendi inẓeɣ.
\v 18 Mammec issmuhrut řmar! Tiḥimriwin n ifunasen d tfunasin qqiment ḥayar, maɣar war ɣarsent bu ddemnet n tarewsa! Uřa d tiḥimriwin n wuǧi fnant.”
\m 
\v 19 “Ɣarek i ttřaɣiɣ necc, \add a\add* SIDI, minzi timessi tecca ddmani n řexřa u yijj n uceɛɛař aqa issecmeḍ marra ticejjura n yiyyar.”
\v 20 Ura d řmař deg iyyar sekkʷḍen-dd ɣarek, minzi tɣezratin uẓɣent u timessi tecca ddmani n řexřa.”
\b
\b
\c 2
\m 
\v 1 “Suḍem deg uyicc n icarri di Ṣihyun, ṣudem dayes s jjehd x wedrar inu iqeddsen, jjem marra imezdaɣ n temmurt ad arjijen, maɣar yudes wass n SIDI, \add wah,\add* aqa-t yudes. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Yuw. 1:15; Ṣaf. 1:14, 15\x*
\v 2 Ijj n wass n taǧest d tubbarcent, ijj n wass n iseynuten u n yijj n useynu ibbumbes. Am tuffut n řḥař igguren x idurar ad dd-yas ijj n řgens d ameqqran u ijhed! Am wanita ɛemmarṣ war iǧi zi mecḥař uya u awarni as war ittiři ɛawed, deg iseggʷusa \add awarni as\add* zi jjiř ař jjiř nneɣni.
\v 3 Zzat i wudem nnes tᵉttett tmessi u awarni as icemmeḍ uceɛɛař. Zzates tammurt tegga am weḥwic n Ɛadn, \add maca\add* awarni as aqa \add din\add* ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen. War izemmar ad zzayes injem.
\v 4 Ccuf nsen am ccuf n yiysan u nitni ttazzřen am yiysan n tazřa.
\v 5 Am uqarqeb n ikarruten n umenɣi x tqiccitin n idurar, \add ammu\add* neggzen nitni, am řḥess n uceɛɛař n tmessi ittetten iɣeǧ, am yijj n řgens ijehden isedden i umenɣi.
\v 6 Zzat i wudem nsen ttarjijen řegnus, marra iɣembab dewřen d icemřařen.”
\m 
\v 7 “Nitni ttazzřen am ayt n bu-teɣruḍt, am yiɛeskariyyen ttgeɛɛaden nitni řḥiḍ, kuř ijj iggur abrid nnes u nitni war dd-tteffɣen ca zeg umesruq nsen.
\v 8 Uřa d ijjen war iɛarren wenneɣni, kuř bu-ṭeɣřuḍt \add iggur\add* deg webrid nnes, u waxxa nitni wḍan s lansa, war ttemsbeɛɛiden
\v 9 Nitni weṭṭan x tendint, ttazzřen x řḥiḍ, ttgeɛɛaden ɣar tudrin, ttadfen zi řekwaza am uxewwan.
\v 10 Tᵉttarjiji temmurt zzat i wudem nsen, ijenwan ttenhezzan, tafuct d tziri bbarcnent u itran arrin tafawt nsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Ica. 13:10; Ḥiz. 32:7\x*
\v 11 SIDI yarra tmijja nnes ad teffeɣ zzat i řɛeskar nnes, maɣar řɛeskar nnes d ameqqran aṭṭas, maɣar s ṣṣulṭa ittkemmař Netta awař nnes, maɣar ass n SIDI d ameqqran, issaggʷad aṭṭas. Wi izemmaren ad t iksi?” \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Irm. 30:7; Ɛam. 5:18; Ṣaf. 1:15\x*
\b
\s1 Ařaɣi i ttubet d uẓummi d wecḍan
\m 
\v 12 “Uřa řexxu \add ɛad\add* iqqar SIDI, ɛeqbem-dd ɣari s marra uř nwem, s uẓummi u s imeṭṭawen u s tɣuyyit n wecḍan. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Irm. 4:1\x*
\v 13 Carrgem uř nwem, war iǧi arruḍ nwem, u dewřem-dd ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nwem, maɣar Netta d aḥnin d arḥim u ɣares ttasiɛ n řxaḍar d tmexsiwt tameqqrant icewwaren u Netta ineddem x řɣar. \x ◘ \xo 2:13 \xt Uf. 34:6; Izhd. 86:15; Yun. 4:2\x*
\v 14 Wi issnen aqa Netta ad dd-idweř ad indem u ad yejj ict n lbaraka. awarni as: ict n tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u ict n tewbibt n useyyeb i SIDI, AREBBI nwem.” \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Yun. 3:9\x*
\b
\m 
\v 15 “Suḍem deg uyicc n icarri di Ṣihyun, qeddsem ijj n uẓummi, barrḥem s yijj n umuni ifarz. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Yuw. 1:14\x*
\v 16 Smunem řgens, qeddsem agraw \add n řgens\add*, jarwem imɣaren, smunem iḥenjiren imeẓyanen uřa d iseyman nni ɛad itteṭṭḍen. Ejj muřay ad iffeɣ zeg wexxam nnes n daxeř d tesřit zeg uqiḍun nnes.
\v 17 Jjem ikehhanen, imsexxaren n SIDI, ad run jar wesqif d uɛalṭar u jjem i-ten ad inin: ‘Sɛizz x řgens nnec, \add a\add* SIDI, u war ttejji tasɣart nnec ad zzayes stehezzan u ad tt ggen d ijj n řmatal jar asen, \add jar\add* řegnus. Mayemmi ɣa qqaren jar řegnus: Mani iǧa AREBBI nsen?’”\x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Izhd. 42:11; 79:10; 115:2\x*
\b
\s1 Mammec i dd-yarra SIDI x wenni d as ittẓaǧan
\m 
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* yusem SIDI x temmurt nnes u iḥinn x řgens nnes.
\v 19 SIDI yarra-dd, inna i řgens nnes: “Xzar, Necc ssekkeɣ awem-dd imendi d binu n jdid d zzect, ḥima kenniw ad zzaysen tejjawnem, u Necc war kenniw tticeɣ ɛad i useḥqar jar řegnus.
\v 20 Wenni \add dd-yusin\add* zi ccamal ad t ssiggʷejeɣ xawem u ad t ssuffɣeɣ ɣar ict n temmurt yuẓɣen tᵉttwakeḥḥeḍ. Aɣembub nnes \add ad t ssuffɣeɣ\add* ɣar řebḥar n ccarq u ḍeffar nnes ɣar řebḥar di ccarq. Ad tgeɛɛed arriḥet nnes, \add wah,\add* ad tgeɛɛed arriḥet n terṣuḍi nnes, waxxa netta aqa igga timesřayin timeqqranin.”
\m 
\v 21 “War tteggʷed, \add a\add* tammurt, sřiwřew d tfarḥed, maɣar SIDI igga timesřayin timeqqranin.
\v 22 War tteggʷedem ca, \add a\add* řmař n yiyyar, maɣar ddmani n řexřa ad zzeyzun, ticejjura ad wcent řɣiǧet nsent, tazayart d wartu n tazart ad wcen řɣiǧet nsen.
\v 23 Iḥenjiren n Ṣihyun, sřiwřewem u farḥem di SIDI, AREBBI nwem, maɣar Netta ad awem iwc Amseɣɣar n tsegda u Netta ad dd-issehwa anẓar i kenniw, anẓar n řexrif d wenẓar n arbiɛ ɣar umezwaru \add n yimir\add*. \f ◼ \fr 2:23 \fk řexrif\ft - niɣ ‘amwan’. \fk arrbiɛ\ft - niɣ ‘tafsut’. \fk imir\ft - ixs ad yini s Tɛibranit ‘lfaṣl’ amecnaw ‘anebdu’ d ‘arrbiɛ’.\f*
\v 24 Inedrar ad ccuren s imendi u tisarfin \add n uḍiř\add* ad ssefyent s binu n jdid d zzect.
\v 25 Necc ad awem xeřfeɣ iseggʷusa i ccint tmurɣi - bu-weřsaḥ d bu-uṣarḍ d bu-weqḍeɛ - řɛeskar inu ameqqran nni ssekkeɣ jar awem. \x ◘ \xo 2:25 \xt Yuw. 1:4\x*
\v 26 Kenniw ad teccem ař ɣa tfeyyḍem, ař ɣa tejjawnem u kenniw ad tṣebbḥem Isem n SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni akidwem iggin řeɛjeb, uca řgens inu ɛemmarṣ ad iseḍḥa ɛad.
\v 27 Kenniw ad tessnem aqa Necc di řwest n Israil i ǧiɣ u d Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war \add din\add* iǧi ḥed nneɣni u řgens inu war ittseḍḥa ɛemmarṣ i řebda.”
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Asfarreɣ n Arruḥ n Arebbi d řeɛřamat n wass n SIDI
\m 
\v 1 “Awarni uya ad imsar, aqa Necc ad zeǧɛeɣ Arruḥ inu x marra bnadem u iḥenjiren nwem d yessitwem ad nebban, iwessura nwem ad urjan tirja u iḥudriyyen nwem ad ẓaren iweḥḥan. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt Ica. 44:3; Ḥiz. 39:29; Řex. 2:17\x*
\v 2 Deg wussan nni Necc ad farrɣeɣ Arruḥ inu uřa x isemɣan u x tiyya.
\v 3 Necc ad ggeɣ lmuɛjizat deg ijenwan u x temmurt: idammen d tmessi d iqellijen n ddexxan.
\v 4 Tafuct ad tedweř d taǧest, u taziri \add ad tedweř\add* d idammen qbeř ma i dd ɣa yas wass ameqqran d issiggʷiden n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Yuw. 4:15\x*
\v 5 Ad imsar aqa kuř ijj wenni i ɣa iřaɣan Isem n SIDI ad injem, maɣar x wedrar n Ṣihyun u di Urcalim ad yiři usenjem am mammec inna SIDI, u ɣar inni yarewřen i xef ɣa iřaɣa SIDI.” \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Ɛub.17; Rum. 10:13\x*
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Řḥukm x řegnus di teɣzurt n Yahucafaṭ
\m 
\v 1 “Maɣar, xzar, deg wussan nni u di řweqt nni, xmi ɣa ssenqeřbeɣ tameḥbast n Yahuda d Urcalim,
\v 2 ad ssmuneɣ marra řegnus, ad ten nedheɣ ɣar Teɣzurt n Yahucafaṭ. Dinni ad akidsen mcarraɛeɣ minzi nitni zuzzaren řgens inu d tesɣart inu jar řegnus u \add minzi\add* nitni bḍan tammurt inu.
\v 3 Nitni ggin taqedduḥt x řgens inu u wcin ijj n weḥram \add d ttexřiṣet\add* i temɣart n farq-ccɣeř u ict n teḥramt temmenz i binu, ḥima nitni zemmaren ad swen.
\m 
\v 4 U ɛawed, min ɣarwem akidi, Ṣur d Ṣidun d marra jjwayeh n Filicit. Ma texsem ad ayi txeǧṣem min ggiɣ? Mařa texsem ad ayi txeǧṣem, Necc ad ssɛeqbeɣ deɣya u s tazřa min teggim x izeǧifen nwem,
\v 5 minzi kenniw tekksim nnuqart d wureɣ inu u \add minzi\add* kenniw tiwyem řeqcuɛ inu yiɣřan ɣar tzawiyyin nwem.
\v 6 Kenniw tᵉzzenzem iḥenjiren n Yahuda d iḥenjiren n Urcalim i iḥenjiren n Yawan, ḥima ad ten tessiggʷejem x temmurt nsen.
\v 7 Xzar, Necc ad ten ssekkareɣ zeg wemcan mani ten tezzenzem u ad ssɛeqbeɣ min teggim x izeǧifen nwem.
\v 8 Ad zzenzeɣ iḥenjiren nwem d yessitwem deg ufus n iḥenjiren n Yahuda u yina ad ten zzenzen i Isaba’iyyen, ijj n řgens iggʷej aṭṭas, maɣar SIDI aqa issiweř.”
\m 
\v 9 “Řaɣam aya jar řegnus, qeddsem amenɣi, sekkarem ayt n bu-teɣruḍt, jjem marra iɛeskariyyen ad dd-qarrben, ad geɛɛden \add i umenɣi\add*.
\v 10 Ḥeddem dduzan nwem d řesyuf uřa d řemwas nwem n wezbar \add ař ɣa dewřen\add* d fřitcat, ejj wenni iḍeɛfen ad yini: ‘Necc d bu-teɣruḍt!’
\v 11 Azzřem u tasem-dd, \add a\add* marra řegnus i dd-innḍen. Sneddeh ɣar dinni, \add a\add* SIDI, ayt nnec n bu-teɣruḍt!
\v 12 Jjem řegnus ad kkaren ad geɛɛden ɣar Teɣzurt n Yahucafaṭ. Maɣar dinni ad qqimeɣ Necc ḥima ad carrɛeɣ marra řegnus i-dd-innḍen.
\v 13 Ggem amjar dayes, maɣar ṣṣabet tenngʷa, asem-dd, hwam, minzi tasirt n uḍiř teccur u ṣṣwarej n tsirt feyyḍen, maɣar taɛeffant nsen d tameqqrant.” \x ◘ \xo 4:13 \xt Asa. 14:15\x*
\b
\m 
\v 14 “Ibarruten, ibarruten di Teɣzurt n Teřwiḥt Itteḥruǧuḍen n Usarwet, maɣar ass n SIDI yudes, di Teɣzurt n Teřwiḥt Itteḥruǧuḍen i Usarwet.
\v 15 Tafuct d tziri bbarcnent, itran arrin tafawt nsen. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt Yuw. 2:10; 3:4. \x*
\v 16 SIDI ad izehhar zi Ṣihyun u ad yarr tmijja nnes ad ittwaseř zi Urcalim \add ařami\add* ijenwan d temmurt ad arjijen, \add maca\add* SIDI d adurri i řgens nnes d lburj i ayt n Israil.”
\b
\m 
\v 17 “Ad tessnem, aqa Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, wenni izeddɣen x Ṣihyun, adrar inu iqeddsen u \add tandint n\add* Urcalim ad tiři tqeddes. Ɛemmarṣ ad tt cuqen \add ɛad\add* ibarraniyyen.” \x ◘ \xo 4:17 \xt Asa. 21:27\x*
\b
\m 
\v 18 “Deg wass nni ad imsar aqa idurar ad udmen s binu ẓemmen t jdid u tiwririn ad ssefyent s uɣi d marra tiɣezratin n Yahuda ad daysen ttazzřen waman u yict n tařa ad tedduqqez di Taddart n SIDI, ad tfeyyeḍ teɣzurt n Ciṭṭim. \x ◘ \xo 4:18 \xt Ɛam. 9:13\x*
\v 19 Miṣra ad tedweř d ict n temmurt ittwareddǧen u Idum d ict n temmurt ixřan zi ssibbet n lɛunf \add i ggin ḍidd i\add* ayt n Yahuda nni zi ssizzřen nitni idammen imezdagen di temmurt nsen.
\v 20 \add Tammurt n\add* Yahuda \add maca\add* ad teqqim i řebda u Urcalim zi jjiř ař jjiř.
\v 21 Necc ad ḥesbeɣ idammen nsen, inni tyɣa ḥessabeɣ war izdigen, d imezdagen.
\m Uca SIDI ad izdeɣ di Ṣihyun.” 
